> I was wondering if anyone can be of assistance.  My delima is that I can
> zsh.exe for NT but it does not source in any of my start files.  What
> must I do to get it to source files during startup.

Settings / Control Panel / System / Environment.  Then make sure that you
have a HOME environment variable set to point to the directory where your
startup files live.  At least, that's all I had to do.

